They aren't anxious
to come back again.

1588
01:38:33,429 --> 01:38:36,479
Next time I see 'em, they're
in their Sunday best,

1589
01:38:36,562 --> 01:38:37,737
if you get me.

1590
01:38:39,957 --> 01:38:43,004
He was a great man
and a good friend.

1591
01:38:44,570 --> 01:38:47,229
He's been doing our
books for 23 years

1592
