had loose ends

1648
01:41:26,341 --> 01:41:28,125
to tie up in Omaha.

1649
01:41:29,344 --> 01:41:31,911
Chuck didn't really miss
them, if he was honest.

1650
01:41:32,912 --> 01:41:35,006
His Zaydee hated a fuss

1651
01:41:35,089 --> 01:41:37,352
almost as much as
he hated a crowd.

1652
